parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: HoneypotImageName
parameters.description: The name of the honeypot image.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and response. Valid values:

*   **zh**: Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: NodeId
parameters.description: The ID of the management node.

parameters.name: NodeName
parameters.description: The name of the management node.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: 20. If you leave this parameter empty, 20 entries are returned on each page.

> We recommend that you do not leave this parameter empty.

parameters.name: PresetName
parameters.description: The custom name of the honeypot template.
